cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on activity detection in videos using person/vehicle detections and action localization. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with extended videos and the use of different tubelet generation methods. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses model decomposition methods and late fusion of results. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with automated activity detection in surveillance videos. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is unlikely as the paper does not mention any security or cryptography-related topics.
